Jeanetta Riley, 35, a mother-of-three daughters was shot and killed by two police officers on July 8, 2014 in Sandpoint, Idaho . 
 She was addicted to meth and alcohol and was taken to Bronner General Hospital by her husband, Shane, after making threats to kill herself . 
 While outside of the hospital, she pulled the knife from under her car seat with a three-and-a-half inch blade . 
 In the video she is repeatedly told to put down the knife but responds 'f*** you no' and 'bring it on' before she walks towards officers